mods.description:
Add striped clothing:
- Stockings (2 options) (only for digitigrade feet);
- Long Gloves (2 options);
- Panties.
Sold in the laundry in the vendomat.

Changelog:
- Added stockings without socks, gloves without fingers;
- Stockings became narrower (I redrew them).

[b][color=red]**Warning!**[/color][/b]
Old clothes will be deleted, you can save them and change the values in the save file using Notepad++:
1. Call the search (Ctrl+F);
2. Select the `Replace` tab;
3. Enter in the first line `"id": "Phobos_Striped_Stockings"` or `"id": "Phobos_Striped_Long_Gloves"` , in the bottom `"id": "Phobos_Striped_Stockings_1"`  or `"id": "Phobos_Striped_Gloves_1"` ;
4. Click the `Replace All` button;
5. Repeat with other items, if any.

[b](/!\ Requires FoxLib,   Requires Chastity Cage Flat Remix /!\)[b]

[b]INMATE GENERATION FINALLY WORKS, HURRAH![/b]
Make random NPCs spawn with permanent or non-permanent chastity cages. It's customizable: you are able to change rules for inmates, guards, engineers, nurses, as well as for specific gender. You can also choose a chance of spawning a flat and/or permanent cage variants. Currently doesn't affect any non-random NPCs. Additionally, adds chastity police mechanic - staff can now stop player or NPC inmates who somehow got rid of their cages, including the player. Mod options are available thanks to FoxLib (go to the [Mods Options] in the main menu)

Changelog: 
• Inmates now generate with cages as intended;
• Player and NPCs can now be put into non permanent cage upon inspection (according to chance in mod's settings);
• Doing obedience training instead of starting the game with male chastity perk also allows for cage inspections to the player;
• Removed generation in dungeons, for now, as the code has to be reworked further to account for that part of gameplay.



